OL,6,FMr Cornock said: "What's changed in
OL,7,Fthat time is that now I'm seeing all
OL,8,Fsorts of refuse, trailer loads of
OL,9,Ftyres, a kitchen, even a sofa. It's
OL,10,Fbecome almost like a tidal wave and
OL,11,Fyou clear out but then another month
OL,12,Flater there's more rubbish."
OL,14,FUnder the Youtube account 'The Funky
OL,15,FFarmer', Mr Cornock films incidents of
OL,16,Ffly-tipping and posts them online. In
OL,17,Fone instance an entire kitchen can be
OL,18,Fseen scattered across one of his
OL,19,Ffields.
