OL,6,F"It is the household's responsibility
OL,7,Fthat if they are disposing of waste,
OL,8,Fthey do so using licensed companies.
OL,9,FThey can check this on the government
OL,10,Fwebsite."
OL,12,FThe NFU estimates two thirds of
OL,13,Ffarmers have been affected by fly-
OL,14,Ftipping, with the government
OL,15,Fdescribing the practice as
OL,16,F'inexcusable'.
