OL,6,F"We encourage our residents to report
OL,7,Fincidents of fly-tipping so they can
OL,8,Fbe thoroughly investigated, and where
OL,9,Fevidence allows, we will bring those
OL,10,Fwho have committed offences before the
OL,11,Fcourts.
OL,13,F"We always pursue fly-tip related
OL,14,Fprosecutions through the courts and
OL,15,Four award-winning environmental
OL,16,Fenforcement team has a 100 per cent
OL,17,Frecord of securing successful
OL,18,Fprosecutions for this type of offence.
